DESCRIPTION >
    Returns event_id values for a given org (and optional user) — used by the GDPR erasure endpoint.

NODE endpoint
SQL >
  %
  SELECT event_id
  FROM llm_events_filtered
  WHERE org_id = {{ String(org_id, '') }}
    {% if defined(user_id) and user_id != '' %}
    AND user_id = {{ String(user_id, '') }}
    {% end %}
    AND timestamp >= {{ DateTime(from_date, '2000-01-01 00:00:00') }}
    AND timestamp <= {{ DateTime(to_date,   '2099-12-31 23:59:59') }}
